&gt;&gt; Hi.

00:22:57.740 --> 00:22:58.740
&gt;&gt; Hi.

00:22:59.740 --> 00:23:02.273
&gt;&gt; The protagonist in Evensong began
in Father Melancholy's daughter,

00:23:01.740 --> 00:23:03.873
are there any other characters
from your older books that you'd

00:23:03.740 --> 00:23:03.766
like to revisit and
resurrect in a future work?

00:23:06.780 --> 00:23:07.780


00:23:07.850 --> 00:23:08.003
&gt;&gt; No, but I wold like to resurrect
Magda and the good husband,

00:23:11.830 --> 00:23:13.763
she's dead, even in the book.

00:23:13.830 --> 00:23:16.496
And there are certain
kinds of characters

00:23:17.850 --> 00:23:21.250
that you don't finish with,
like Unfinished Desires,

00:23:22.230 --> 00:23:25.030
there is a character
called Mod [phonetic],

00:23:26.910 --> 00:23:29.376
who's troubled right
into her old age.

00:23:30.160 --> 00:23:33.626
So she didn't get a start
in writing until she is 70.

00:23:35.920 --> 00:23:40.720
And I'm doing another character like
that in my new book as a girl of 10,

00:23:45.780 --> 00:23:48.380
and she's alone with
her summer guardian

00:23:50.510 --> 00:23:52.443
who is a very peculiar woman.

00:23:52.510 --> 00:23:55.043
And that's the Turn
of the Screw slant.

00:23:55.250 --> 00:23:56.250
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:23:57.250 --> 00:23:58.450
&gt;&gt; You're welcome.

00:23:59.250 --> 00:24:00.250
&gt;&gt; Hi.

00:24:01.250 --> 00:24:02.250
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:24:03.250 --> 00:24:05.650
&gt;&gt; I have more of a comment and
appreciation than a question, and--

00:24:05.250 --> 00:24:06.383
&gt;&gt; Oh, thank you.

00:24:07.250 --> 00:24:09.080
&gt;&gt; I guess I've been an avid
reader since I was six or seven,

00:24:09.420 --> 00:24:12.420
and probably been an
avid reader of your works

00:24:13.310 --> 00:24:15.043
since you started writing.

00:24:15.310 --> 00:24:16.443
&gt;&gt; Oh, thank you.

00:24:17.310 --> 00:24:19.043
&gt;&gt; And have just-- am so--

00:24:19.310 --> 00:24:20.203
you're what inspired me to come
down here in the mall today.

00:24:22.350 --> 00:24:23.350
And I just--

00:24:24.370 --> 00:24:24.676
&gt;&gt; [Inaudible] with you
back to the convent.

00:24:26.930 --> 00:24:27.930
[ Laughter ]

00:24:28.930 --> 00:24:32.930
&gt;&gt; So I'm just delighted to see
your progress, and follow it.

